{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20260429/photo/bkn-20260429150333914-0429_00992_001_01p.jpg?20260429150802\" alt=\"\"><p>尹錫悅妨礙逮捕二審宣判。（電視畫面）</p><p>南韓前總統尹錫悅涉嫌妨礙逮捕案二審周三（29日）宣布，被判有期徒刑7年。</p><p>上一則 下一則</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T07:20:57.061001+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":63,"images":1,"source":"東網 國際","fallback":"none"}}